name: Middle intermediate IT layer

classes.name: Device
classes.description: A device of an IT infrastructure
classes.geometry: async function vizRep(gc){ await gc.setVariable('name', await gc.dynval('7d3c4c5e-68e5-4b6a-96be-2f3f34ad392a', await gc.get_current_class_instance_uuid()), false); await gc.setVariable('x_rel', -0.4, true); await gc.setVariable('y_rel', 0.1, true); await gc.setVariable('z_rel', -0.05, true); let map= 'data:image/svg+xml;base64,'; let icon = map; await gc.graphic_cube(1, 0.8, 0.02, 'lightgrey', map); await gc.graphic_text(await gc.getVariableValue('x_rel'), await gc.getVariableValue('y_rel'), await gc.getVariableValue('z_rel'), 0.15, 'black', await gc.getVariableValue('name'), 'x_rel', 'y_rel', 'z_rel'); }

classes.name: Wall
classes.description: A wall element of an IT infrastructure representing power supply or/and internet access
classes.geometry: async function vizRep(gc){ await gc.setVariable('name', await gc.dynval('7d3c4c5e-68e5-4b6a-96be-2f3f34ad392a', await gc.get_current_class_instance_uuid()), false); await gc.setVariable('x_rel', -0.4, true); await gc.setVariable('y_rel', 0.1, true); await gc.setVariable('z_rel', -0.05, true); let map= 'data:image/svg+xml;base64,'; let icon = map; await gc.graphic_cube(1, 0.7, 0.02, 'lightgrey', map); await gc.graphic_text(await gc.getVariableValue('x_rel'), await gc.getVariableValue('y_rel'), await gc.getVariableValue('z_rel'), 0.15, 'black', await gc.getVariableValue('name'), 'x_rel', 'y_rel', 'z_rel'); }
